{
    "title": "Capitu",
    "artist": "Luiz Tatit",
    "composer": "Luiz Tatit",
    "lyricsHtml": "\nIntro: <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">De um lado vem você com seu jeitinho</span>\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Hábil, hábil, hábil    E pronto!</span>\n                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Me conquista com seu dom</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">De outro esse seu site petulante</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">WWW   Ponto   Poderosa ponto com</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em\">Em</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D/F#\">D/F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É esse o seu modo de ser ambíguo</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sábio, sábio</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E todo encanto, canto, canto</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Raposa e sereia da terra e do mar</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Na tela e no ar</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Você é virtualmente amada amante</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Você real é ainda mais tocante</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>      (X)\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Não há quem não se encante</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um método de agir que é tão astuto</span>\n                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Com jeitinho alcança tudo, tudo, tudo</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É só se entregar, é não resistir, é capitular</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                            :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Capitu                                  :</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                  :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A ressaca dos mares                     :</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A sereia do sul                         :   {refrão 1}</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                  :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Captando os olhares                     :</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                   :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Nosso totem tabu                                 :</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                 :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A mulher em milhares    Capitu          :</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">{volta tudo até o (X) e continua daqui}</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">No site o seu poder provoca o ócio, o ócio</span>\n                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um passo para o vício, o vício</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É só navegar, é só te seguir, e então naufragar</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                            :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Capitu                                  :</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                  :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Feminino com arte                                :</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                    :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A traição atraente                               :   {refrão 2}</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                  :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um capítulo à parte                     :</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#m\">F#m</span>                   :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quase vírus ardente                     :</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A\">A</span>                 :\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Imperando no site        Capitu         :</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">{volta tudo do ínicio e refrão 1 e refrão 2 e fim}</span>\n",
